    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though you may notice some typical wear such as minor oil seepage and a slightly loud exhaust. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dents, while the interior shows clear signs of use, including some staining on the upholstery and wear on the steering wheel. It has been recently serviced to ensure it is road-ready, making it a functional choice for daily commuting or as a secondary work vehicle.",
