    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Mechanically superlative and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this offering represents a premier acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality and distinction.",
