    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I'm parting with this absolute gem, and let me tell you, it is stunning. I have babied this car since the day I got it\u2014it's basically in showroom condition! It looks and smells brand new, with a spotless interior and a shine that'll turn heads everywhere you go. It drives like a dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. I\u2019m looking for a buyer who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by and see it for yourself; you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 45900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2009 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) finished in Basalt Black Metallic. This example features the coveted MA1.01 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six, benefiting from Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) and the elimination of the IMS bearing architecture found in previous generations. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle, delivering linear torque through a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. Chassis dynamics are sharpened by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono Package Plus, ensuring optimized throttle mapping and damping. This vehicle exhibits a pristine DME overrev report and retains original factory cosmoline on the undercarriage. Recent comprehensive maintenance includes a full ignition coil service, drive belt replacement, and a transaxle fluid flush using high-viscosity OEM lubricants. A mechanically superlative specimen for the discerning purist.",
